# Serve the prerendered shell for dynamic client routes so a direct
# hit (refresh, shared link) hydrates instead of 404ing; SolidStart's
# router picks up the real path from the URL. Format is
# `<source> <destination> <status>`, status 200 = rewrite. Target
# the literal `<route>/index.html` file: any bare or slashed
# directory form triggers Workers Assets' trailing-slash redirect,
# which escapes the rewrite and clobbers the original URL.

/studio/*  /studio/  200
